title: Kristin Cavallari: 'I've Read Too Many Books' To Vaccinate
description:
Former 'Hills' star Kristin Cavallari joins us on-set to discuss why she thinks vaccines aren't for her and her role on E! Network's new half-hour lifestyle show 'Fabulist,' as co-host alongside clothing designer & 'Fashion Star' contestant, Orly Shani.
